description:
Happy Holidays from Unqualified! This week's guest is one of the kindest people in Hollywood: Zachary Levi (Chuck, Tangled, Thor)! In this episode, the gang covers everything from the rise and fall of stars, early careers, social media, and rejection. They also put Zach up to the test with some deal breakers and play a new game called “Name The Disney Mental Disorder!” Later, they call Haley, who’s on the fence about asking her boyfriend of a year to move across the country for her, and Meg, who’s nervous about attending a big work event because SMALL TALK IS THE WORST GUYS.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
